Package: locateip
Title: Locate IP Addresses with 'ip-api'
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Judith", "Bourque", , "judith.bourque.2@ulaval.ca", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-3653-1530"))
Description: Download Internet Protocol (IP) address location and more from the 'ip-api' application programming interface (API) <[https://ip-api.com/]https://ip-api.com/>. The package makes it easy to get the latitute, longitude, country, region, and organisation associated to the provided IP address. The information is conveniently returned in a rectangular format.
